parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag recall repair can lead to the airbag deploying unexpectedly or not deploying at all in the event of a crash, posing a risk to the driver and passengers.

the airbag deploys unexpectedly
or the airbag does not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of available parts for the recall repair can leave vehicles unrepaired, posing a risk to drivers and passengers.
